User Stories: [KOK-34], [KOK-37], [KOK-46]

Time: 25m

Platforms: iOS 7 iPhone

Start: 6/12/14 12:30 a.m.

Notes:
Users should be able to add venue properties to their venues.
Users shouldn't be able to alter venue properties to other venues.
Users should be able to upload venue images to their venues.
Users shouldn't be able to upload venue images to other venues.
Users should be able to make offers at their venues.
Users shouldn't be able to make offers at other venues.

Results:
+	Users can only admin their own venues.
-	Users can add venues on top of others and make fraudulent offers.
-	Offers remain in the offers page after offer deletion.
-	Offers remain in the offers page after venue deletion.
-	App crashes when different time options are selected for the timewall data in the absence of posts.</text></hook></node></node><node CREATED="1402464628626" ID="4hda729ir4vq6n2npc90ang39f" MODIFIED="1402464628626" TEXT="Sprint4"/></node></node></map>